        <div class="col-md-12">
            <h3>Uranium documentation</h3>
            <hr/>
            <p>Uranium is part of the Uranium project. The Uranium project allows you to visualize your own RESTful services.</p>

            <h3>Usage</h3>
            <h4>Run rake task to generate docs</h4>
            <hr/>
            <p>Make sure you have <%= link_to 'rake', 'http://rake.rubyforge.org/', target: "_blank" %> installed.</p>
            <pre>rake uranium:decay['path-to-input.yaml','path-to-output.html']</pre>

            <h4>Generate docs from controller</h4>

            <pre code-highlight="" class="container" code-language="ruby"><%= render template: 'doc/make.html' %></pre>

            <h6>Configuration options</h6>
            <p>The following table shows all the current configuration options and their defaults. The default will be used if you don't supply your own value.</p>

            <table class="table table-striped">
                <thead>
                    <th>Method</th>
                    <th>Option</th>
                    <th>Description</th>
                    <th>Default</th>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td>decay</td>
                        <td>use_layout</td>
                        <td>Parameter is used to enable \ disable the layout design of API methods</td>
                        <td>true</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>

            <h4>Input templates</h4>
            <p>As an input to the generator 2 is acceptable format:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Yaml</li>
                <li>Json</li>
            </ol>

            <h6>Yaml format example</h6>
            <pre code-highlight="" class="container" code-language="yaml"><%= render template: 'doc/template_yaml.html' %></pre>

            <h6>Json format example</h6>
            <pre code-highlight="" class="container" code-language="json"><%= render template: 'doc/template_json.html' %></pre>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>
